{"title":"掌子面（外一首）","authors":["吕海潮"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":7,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌子面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吕海潮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地球的胳膊只伸到这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前面是掌子面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌子面，一个混沌的地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不断剖开的岩石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会嗅到我们身上的热汗味"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘀哒嘀哒的淋头水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴着我们的手关节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘎嘣嘎嘣地响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁传导意志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的心，总是在一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最新延伸出的角落里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们就采掘在这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命拥有常新的感觉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边缘消失了还有边缘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陌生和陌生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不断地认识又不断地放弃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌子面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空间的最末端"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的生命在这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淬火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"取火者雕塑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你必须选择这种姿势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向左、或者向右"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侧身卧着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胳膊肘支起的高度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是身体和地面的距离"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当地球吝啬到极点的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的吝啬就是一种高尚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不肯退缩的神情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对着不肯施舍的岩石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顽固和冷峻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展开对峙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你富有韧性的臂膀挥动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脊梁是一条撕裂黑暗的闪电"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起一伏的肋条下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤，一锹一锹地涌出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"确确实实，有时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卧着比站着更需要勇气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在地球最蹩脚的长廊里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为分娩一轮难产的太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你扭曲成一种美丽"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}